# riscv-tests

The tests in this directory were built from https://github.com/riscv-software-src/riscv-tests commit https://github.com/riscv-software-src/riscv-tests/commit/799d6e807fa1e5b71cc4dace9d75f264c4ff224c .

Toolchain from https://github.com/xpack-dev-tools/riscv-none-elf-gcc-xpack/releases/download/v14.2.0-3/xpack-riscv-none-elf-gcc-14.2.0-3-linux-x64.tar.gz

```bash
$ git clone https://github.com/riscv/riscv-tests
$ cd riscv-tests
$ git submodule update --init --recursive
$ autoconf
$ ./configure --prefix=$RISCV/target
$ make
$ make install
```

Modify makefiles if needed. Only ISA is in the folder.